source: TEXT_SUBCTS711_02387_WOODWAILERCAPTAIN01556_000_000<tab>Well met, adventurer. Thanks to your diligence, we have expanded the scope of our reconnaissance missions in the ruins. Unfortunately, we have yet to find any clues as to who, or what, is the source of our problems.
target:
TEXT_SUBCTS711_02387_WOODWAILERCAPTAIN01556_000_000おお、)) (( )) 02 /var>、よく来てくれた！
君のおかげで、地下迷宮の調査も徐々に進んではおるが、
いまだ、黒幕の所在は不明のまま……。

source: TEXT_SUBCTS711_02387_WOODWAILERCAPTAIN01556_000_001<tab>You claimed the undead spoke of a robed figure, correct? Perhaps this is the foul sorcerer who gave birth to the palace and its inhabitants.
target:
TEXT_SUBCTS711_02387_WOODWAILERCAPTAIN01556_000_001君が倒した死者がつぶやいた「魔術師」という言葉……。
恐らくは、地下迷宮を造り上げた黒幕を指すのだろう。

source: TEXT_SUBCTS711_02387_WOODWAILERCAPTAIN01556_000_002<tab>To not only create such a labyrinth, but to fill it with the souls of so many innocents... We are dealing with a foe possessed of dark and terrible power.
target:
TEXT_SUBCTS711_02387_WOODWAILERCAPTAIN01556_000_002これほどの規模の地下迷宮を造り上げただけではなく、
死者を復活させ使役する術をも使いこなすとは……。
敵は、どれほどの力を持っているというのか……。

source: TEXT_SUBCTS711_02387_WOODWAILERCAPTAIN01556_000_003<tab>It pains me to burden you, but on behalf of the Wood Wailers I would ask that you seek out and put an end to the one behind all this. I can think of none more capable for the task at hand.
target:
TEXT_SUBCTS711_02387_WOODWAILERCAPTAIN01556_000_003君の地下迷宮への習熟具合は、我ら調査隊の誰よりも上……。
引き続き地下迷宮に赴き、更なる深淵へと至る道を探し出し、
「魔術師」の凶行を食い止めてほしい……！

source: TEXT_SUBCTS711_02387_WOODWAILERCAPTAIN01556_000_004<tab>My men have not the strength to stand with you in the ruins, but rest assured we shall do all we can to support you here at Quarrymill. Now go─drive out the evil of the Palace of the Dead, before the deceased should find their way out into the Twelveswood.
target:
TEXT_SUBCTS711_02387_WOODWAILERCAPTAIN01556_000_004君にばかり、無理を強いてすまないな……。
エ・ウナ様も我ら鬼哭隊も、君への尽力は惜しまない所存だ。
森の全域に「魔術師」の脅威が及ぶ前に、どうか頼んだぞ！

source: TEXT_SUBCTS711_02387_SYSTEM_000_010<tab>You can now explore beyond floor 50 of the Palace of the Dead.
target:
TEXT_SUBCTS711_02387_SYSTEM_000_010「地下迷宮 死者の宮殿」の、
「B51」以降に挑戦できるようになりました。
引き続き、「鬼哭隊の調査隊長」から挑戦が可能です。

source: TEXT_SUBCTS711_02387_WOODWAILERCAPTAIN01556_000_100<tab>You have done well to complete such a thorough survey of the ruins, but the road ahead is ever more treacherous. Before you proceed, I would know for certain you are duly prepared for the challenges ahead.
target:
TEXT_SUBCTS711_02387_WOODWAILERCAPTAIN01556_000_100地下迷宮の探索には、相当の危険が伴う……。
こうして出向いてくれたことは感謝するが、
まずは、戦闘の身支度を整えてもらえるかね？

source: TEXT_SUBCTS711_02387_SYSTEM_000_110<tab>In order to proceed with this quest, you must first meet the following requirements:
target:
TEXT_SUBCTS711_02387_SYSTEM_000_110本クエストを進行するためには、
以下の条件を満たす必要があります。

source: TEXT_SUBCTS711_02387_SYSTEM_000_111<tab>※ You must be at least level 17 with a Disciple of War or Magic.
target:
TEXT_SUBCTS711_02387_SYSTEM_000_1111.現在のクラス・ジョブが、レベル17以上の、
　ファイター、もしくはソーサラーである。
